	These entitlements are needed for the external tools to be launchable from the main GUI,
	as well as to get access to user-selected folders.
	See: https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/Miscellaneous/Reference/EntitlementKeyReference/Chapters/EnablingAppSandbox.html
-->
